Another change by BS

For Polymer & Polyester business, Inquiry is the first stage of transaction recording. Inquiry is recorded in CRM system. Inquiry document captures information about the requirements from the prospective customer namely customer details, price, materials and the quantity. Inquiry document once created goes for two level of approval in the system. Once the inquiry is approved, it is auto-converted into a contract and is interfaced in with SAP.
Observation
